snippet: Serena Williams finished her last U.S. Open tune-up in style by blowing away Serbian Ana Ivanovic 6-4 6-1 to win her first title at the Western and Southern Open in Cincinnati on Sunday....

headline.print_headline: Serena Wins Cincinnati Title in Final U.S. Open Tune-Up
headline.main: Serena Wins Cincinnati Title in Final U.S. Open Tune-Up

lead_paragraph: Serena Williams finished her last U.S. Open tune-up in style by blowing away Serbian Ana Ivanovic 6-4 6-1 to win her first title at the Western and Southern Open in Cincinnati on Sunday.
